Download the files to a linux system. On the Linux system run "make" to compile readperfstats.c. To test the program run
"./readperfstats" to display the system information in the following format:
--- Memory Stats ---
Free Memory = 252464 KB
Used Memory = 762336 KB
Total Memory = 1014800 KB
Memory Utilization = 75.12%
...

The source code is at http://github.com/bjwbell/CSC239-Linux-Team/archives/master 